Zava crept quietly in the engine room of Phobia's ship. She went up 
to the main engine, and pressed a button on her arm. A device popped 
out and she caught it. She placed it on the engine, and pressed a few 
button. This is what it said.

2:00...1:59....1:58..

Zava laughed in a quiet tone.

"Hehehehe....They destroyed their own base, but they won't escape the 
fire...."

Zava pulled out her blasters and got her optics ready. Anyone who 
tried to come in here would get blown to pieces.
